&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;WHO WE ARE: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Allen Animal Hospital is a well-established small animal practice located in Livonia, Michigan; a suburb in Metro Detroit. Easily accessible off the highway, our location offers the best of both worlds: the charm of a close-knit community with the culture, dining, and entertainment of Detroit only miles away.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Founded by Dr. Vilas Allen in 1966, we’ve delivered compassionate, high-quality veterinary care built on a foundation of education, trust, and relationships for close to six decades. Our experienced and friendly team is proud to serve our community with a strong emphasis on collaboration, communication, and a positive work environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
