&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Associate Veterinarian&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join a team where high‑quality medicine meets an unbeatable lifestyle. At&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Palo Verde Animal Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll practice in a supportive, collaborative environment—right in the heart of&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;beautiful, sunny Phoenix&lt;/strong&gt;, a city known for 300+ days of sunshine, amazing food, stunning desert trails, and year‑round outdoor living.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Phoenix? Why Us?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Located just off&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;SR‑51&lt;/strong&gt;, our central Phoenix location puts you minutes from mountain preserves, vibrant neighborhoods, and some of the best hiking, dining, and cultural spots in the Southwest. We believe in true&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;work‑life balance&lt;/strong&gt;, so you can actually enjoy all that Phoenix offers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monday–Friday only&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Appointments&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;8–11:30 AM&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;1–4 PM&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closed 12–1 PM daily&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;for a mid‑day break&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No weekends, no nights&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Work differently. Live better.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A compassionate veterinarian who values teamwork and excellent patient care&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Someone who loves a calm, collaborative environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A doctor committed to continuous learning and professional growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
