&lt;li&gt;Soft tissue surgery and dental procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Radiography, in‑house lab work, and medical treatments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and support the technical team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong client relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;$135,000–$165,000 base&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plus:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Bonus opportunities + production pay&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also includes:&lt;br&gt;PTO • Medical/Vision/Dental • 401(k) match • Paid parental leave • Disability coverage • CE allowance • VIN membership • Licensure &amp;amp; dues • Uniform allowance • And more&lt;/p&gt;
