&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Associate Veterinarian – Ottawa, IL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Chessie Lane Animal Hospital&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ottawa, Illinois&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Looking for a veterinary role that comes with a genuinely great lifestyle? Chessie Lane Animal Hospital in Ottawa, IL is looking for a full-time Associate Veterinarian to join our friendly, long‑standing team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;ve proudly served the Ottawa community for nearly 30 years, and our commitment to compassionate, high‑quality care earned us the 2023 Times Readers’ Choice Award for Favorite Veterinary Clinic. If you’re hoping to join a clinic where teamwork, positivity, and excellent patient care all matter equally, this may be your perfect fit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You’ll Love Ottawa, IL&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ottawa is one of Illinois’ best-kept secrets—a historic, scenic town located at the confluence of the Illinois and Fox Rivers. Living and working here means enjoying:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Beautiful outdoor spaces including Starved Rock, Matthiessen, and Buffalo Rock State Parks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A welcoming, community‑oriented atmosphere&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A charming downtown full of local restaurants, coffee shops, and boutiques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Affordable living with an easygoing Midwest vibe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Endless opportunities for hiking, kayaking, biking, and weekend adventures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want small‑town warmth with big natural beauty, Ottawa delivers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Our Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Chessie Lane is a supportive, low‑drama workplace where collaboration is valued and kindness is the norm. We work hard, we communicate openly, and we genuinely enjoy each other’s company. Our clinic is fully equipped with:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Digital radiography&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In-house Idexx lab&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ultrasound&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dentistry capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Soft tissue surgery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full GP services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe in giving our doctors the support, tools, and autonomy they need to do their best work while still maintaining work‑life balance.&lt;/p&gt;
